{"search_data": "Chhattisgarh[Rs. 30,000 p.a] CG Rajiv Gandhi Kisan Nyay Yojana 2020 Chhattisgarh for Farmers [2nd Installment]Chhattisgarh Rajiv Gandhi Kisan Nyay Yojana to give Rs. 30,000 p.a to 19 lakh farmers, 2nd installment on 20 August 2020, 1st installment of Rs. 7500 credited earlier through DBT mode in bank accounts of farmers \u0939\u093f\u0902\u0926\u0940 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u092a\u0922\u093c\u0947\u0902Table of Contents  CG Rajiv Gandhi Kisan Nyay Yojana 2020CG Rajiv Gandhi Kisan Nyay Yojana Apply Online FormNo. of Beneficiaries of CG Rajiv Gandhi Kisan Nyay YojanaCG Rajiv Gandhi Kisan Nyay Yojana FAQsCG Rajiv Gandhi Kisan Nyay Yojana 2020In order to ensure appropriate benefit to Annadata (provider of food i.e farmers), the Rajiv Gandhi Kisan Nyay Yojana has been launched. Here is how farmers would be given Rs. 30,000 p.a under Rajiv Gandhi Kisan Nyay Yojana 2020.CG Rajiv Gandhi Kisan Nyay Yojana Apply Online FormJust like other schemes for welfare of farmers, it was believed that the state govt. of Chhattisgarh will invite Rajiv Gandhi Kisan Nyay Yojana application forms. The CG Rajiv Gandhi Kisan Nyay Yojana Apply Online Form were to be invited at the official website of the Chhattisgarh state government or a new dedicated portal for farmers. But due to COVID-19, now there is a change in the procedure. The state govt. has already prepared a list of 19 lakh eligible farmers as CG government has their data. The govt. has allocated Rs. 5700 crore for this purpose to be credited into the eligible farmers account in 4 installments.The 1st installment of CG Rajiv Gandhi Kisaan Nyay Yojana of Rs. 7500 has been credited into farmers account on 21 May 2020 and next installments would be released soon. This scheme is also extended to FY 2019-2020, so all the farmers would be eligible for this scheme for the previous year also. The 2nd installment is going to be credited into farmers account on 20 August 2020 through DBT mode. In this scheme, the state govt. will transfer Rs. 30,000 every year (in 4 installments of Rs. 7500 each) directly into the bank accounts of farmers through DBT mode.No. of Beneficiaries of CG Rajiv Gandhi Kisan Nyay YojanaCM Bhupesh Baghel had announced to provide Rs. 1500 crore as 1st installment for 18,34,834 paddy crops producing farmers. This scheme will provide benefits to 9,53,706 marginal farmers, 5,60,284 small farmers and 3,20,844 big farmers. Now the CM has announced to provide second installment on former PM Rajiv Gandhi\u2019s Birth Anniversary to the same 19 lakh farmers who receives 1st installment.\"\u091c\u094b \u0915\u0939\u093e- \u0938\u094b \u0915\u093f\u092f\u093e\"\u0915\u093e\u0902\u0917\u094d\u0930\u0947\u0938 \u0905\u0927\u094d\u092f\u0915\u094d\u0937\u093e \u092e\u093e\u0928\u0928\u0940\u092f \u0938\u094b\u0928\u093f\u092f\u093e \u0917\u093e\u0902\u0927\u0940 \u091c\u0940 \u090f\u0935\u0902 \u092e\u093e\u0928\u0928\u0940\u092f \u0930\u093e\u0939\u0941\u0932 \u0917\u093e\u0902\u0927\u0940 \u091c\u0940 \u0906\u091c \u0915\u0930\u0947\u0902\u0917\u0947 \"\u0930\u093e\u091c\u0940\u0935 \u0917\u093e\u0902\u0927\u0940 \u0915\u093f\u0938\u093e\u0928 \u0928\u094d\u092f\u093e\u092f \u092f\u094b\u091c\u0928\u093e\" \u0915\u093e \u0936\u0941\u092d\u093e\u0930\u0902\u092d pic.twitter.com/Gs1a4vbueX\u2014 Bhupesh Baghel (@bhupeshbaghel) May 21, 2020 CG Rajiv Gandhi Kisan Nyay Yojana FAQsHere are the most frequently asked questions about the Rajiv Gandhi Kisan Nyay Yojana 2020:-1) What is Rajiv Gandhi Kisan Nyay Yojana? To provide cash directly into the bank accounts of farmers during Coronavirus (COVID-19) lockdown, govt. has started Rajiv Gandhi Kisan Nyay Yojana. Nyay here stands for \u201cNyuntam Aay\u201d meaning minimum wages for farmers.2) What amount each Farmer will Get in CG Kisan Nyay Scheme? Each farmer will get Rs. 30,000 per year under the CG Kisan Nyay Scheme in 4 equal installments.3) How many farmers would be benefited? A total number of 19 lakh farmers would be benefited from this Farmers Nyay Yojana with an outlay of Rs. 5700 crore.4) When this CG Kisan Nyay Scheme 1st / 2nd Phase will Start? The honourable Chief Minister Bhupesh Baghel of Chhattisgarh had started this CG Kisan Nyay Scheme from 21 May 2020. The second phase of CG Kisan Nyay Yojana is going to start from 20 August 2020.5) What is the Amount to be given to Farmers in Rajiv Gandhi Kisan Nyay Yojana Phase 1? In the 1st phase of CG Rajiv Gandhi Kisan Nyay Yojana on 21st May, the state govt. has provided 1st installment of Rs. 7500 to each farmer with an outlay of Rs. 1500 crore. Now the 2nd installment is going to be transferred on 20 August 2020 for which amount is yet to be decided.6) Do Farmers Need to Apply Online / Offline? No there is no need to apply online or offline for CG Rajiv Gandhi Kisan Nyay Yojana 2020. The Chhattisgarh government has already prepared the complete list of 19 lakh farmers.7) Are All Farmers Eligible or there is Specific Crop Requirement? All the farmers who are producing paddy, maize and sugarcane would be eligible for this CG Rajiv Gandhi Kisan Nyay Scheme. It includes small, marginal and big farmers.8) What if My Name is not present in CG Rajiv Gandhi Kisan Nyay Yojana List? Till date, there is no specific criteria defined for any farmer for name inclusion in CG Rajiv Gandhi Kisan Nyay Yojana list of beneficiaries. There are no application / registration forms available as the govt. is already possessing a database of eligible farmers.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/raipur/chhattisgarh-to-release-2nd-instalment-under-nyay-yojana-on-august-20/articleshow/76354789.cms  at  "}